TY  - JOUR
TI  - Quantity Constrained Demand Functions
AU  - Latham, Roger
AB  - [Using duality theory I show that the Tobin-Houthakker conjecture that a reduction in the ration of one good will increase the consumption of unrationed substitutes and diminish the demand for unrationed complements may not hold in disequilibrium situations.]
C1  - Full publication date: Mar., 1980
